title: 119: The Art of Picking A Fight | Ear Biscuits Ep. 119
description:
Rhett & Link dig into their own stories about time they've picked a fight with someone, and go into the Mythical Mail Bag to see what sorts of scraps listeners have found or almost found themselves in as well on this week's Ear Biscuits.
